    public class OpeningBracket
extends Grouping
    An opening bracket operator

    Brackets are used to give priority to some section of expressions.
    A opening bracket serves to mark the beginning of a subexpression that will be later processed as a differen entity. The push is performed by the parent class Grouping, this class is only used to define a name and a priorit
